dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.spec.phy.role.PhysicalResourceRoleDetails
dataStructure.description:
This class captures the semantics of the SpecifiesPhysicalResourceRoles aggregation.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: PhysicalResourceRoleDetails

child.name: typeOfResource
child.description:
This is an array of integers that identifies the type of Resource that this role is targeted to. Each integer value must be unique. The array enables expressions such as "All host devices and all routers" to be built. Values include: 0: any physical resource 1: PhysicalDevices only 2: Hardware only (i.e., components of PhysicalDevices) 3: PhysicalLinks only 4: other resources

This element is generated from an attribute.

This attribute is optional
